public static interface VncCanvas.VncImageListener

The listener interface for receiving vncImage events. The class that is interested in processing a vncImage event implements this interface, and the object created with that class is registered with a component using the component's addVncImageListener method. When the vncImage event occurs, that object's appropriate method is invoked.

See Also:
VncImageEvent
